{
  "texts": [
    "In this framework, we link transfer learning with searching efficiency.",
    "Our DeGCG tunes tokens in discrete space in a manner analogous to how parameters in continuous space are tuned during the pre-training and fine-tuning process.",
    "In this analogy, the counterpart of parameter space is the searching space in DeGCG.",
    "An overview of our method is presented in Fig. 2.",
    "We introduce the first-token searching (FTS) task in the pre-searching stage."
  ]
}